asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Bobbinette Kamu
description:
Bobbinette is a model, actor, and eco-social justice activist. 

A nomad at heart, when she’s not commanding a runway, surfing the dunes, or testifying on climate initiatives and their intersection with native populations at the UN, she resides in Sparks, Nevada.

It is rumored by those who ought to know that she once shot and killed the sun because it was too hot, only to eventually restore it at a slightly more bearable temperature. When asked about her involvement in that particular event, Bobbi declines to answer, but she does admit to long time associations with persons named Cottontail and Sand Rabbit, the legendary troublemakers.

She is a gifted mystic, blessed with insight beyond the mortal realms, loves music, dancing, art museums, costumes, and summer sunset cruises on Lake Lahontan. 

She can be booked for acting and modeling roles through the Cult of Flufthulu.

name: Scratcher
description: I will scratch yours if you scratch me? Pretty cuddly, but also a weapon. Its definitely obvious there is tiger in my nature. I can bite, if you ask nicely. Did you hear that biting can cause babies? Well it can, with me, if you catch my drift? Can you sense the mycelium coursing through my veins? Mycelium Mystics eyes glow purple from the high levels of mycelium in our DNA, and we feel extremely grounded and connected to the universe and all species. We have extraordinary abilities such as strong telepathy between each other, mild telepathy with those without, the ability to alter the mood of others, and the ability to feel when something is going to happen, before it happens. We are seemingly always plugged in to the mycelium network. Some see it as a blessing, while for those all-knowing, it is a sacred guardianship one must master and respect. Some have been lost from overwhelming voices and emotions circulating their minds. Mycelium Mystics are here to protect Fluf World and guide all of the Amethyst Eyes to ensure the fluffle is always happy.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
